---
import ZoneNovaLayout1 from '../../../../layouts/ZoneNovaLayout1.astro';
import FormattedDate from '../../../../components/FormattedDate.astro';
---

<ZoneNovaLayout1 
	title="Leviathan Character Guide - Zone Nova - GachaWiki" 
	description="Complete guide for Leviathan (娇炉-利维坦), the SR Wind pursuit DPS specialist in Zone Nova"
	gameTitle="Leviathan Character Guide"
	showBreadcrumb={true}
	breadcrumbText="Characters"
>
	<Fragment slot="head">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
		<style>
			.back-button {
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				background: var(--bg-primary);
				color: var(--text-primary);
				text-decoration: none;
				padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid var(--amber-glow);
				font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.2);
			}

			.back-button:hover {
				background: var(--amber-glow);
				color: var(--text-inverse);
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.3);
			}

			.back-button:hover .back-arrow {
				transform: translateX(-3px);
			}

			.back-arrow {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				transition: transform 0.3s ease;
			}

			.character-page {
				background: var(--bg-secondary);
				min-height: 100vh;
				padding: 2rem 0;
			}

			.character-container {
				max-width: 1200px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 0 2rem;
			}

			.character-header {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-primary), var(--bg-secondary));
				border-radius: 20px;
				padding: 3rem;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--amber-glow);
				box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.1);
				text-align: center;
				transition: all 0.4s ease;
			}

			.character-header:hover {
				transform: translateY(-4px);
				box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.15);
			}

			.character-image {
				width: 300px;
				height: 300px;
				border-radius: 20px;
				object-fit: cover;
				margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
				display: block;
				box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 172, 193, 0.3);
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
			}

			.character-image:hover {
				transform: scale(1.05);
				box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 172, 193, 0.4);
			}

			.character-title {
				font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
				font-size: 3rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--amber-glow), var(--teal-crystal));
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
				animation: titleGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
			}

			.character-subtitle {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				margin: 0;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.content-section {
				background: var(--bg-primary);
				border-radius: 20px;
				padding: 3rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
				box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.08);
				transition: all 0.4s ease;
				animation: sectionFadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
			}

			.content-section:hover {
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.12);
				border-color: var(--teal-crystal);
			}

			.section-title {
				font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--text-primary);
				margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
				padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber-glow);
				position: relative;
			}

			.section-title::after {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				bottom: -2px;
				left: 0;
				width: 60px;
				height: 2px;
				background: var(--teal-crystal);
			}

			.subsection-title {
				font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--text-primary);
				margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
				padding-left: 1rem;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--amber-glow);
			}

			.skill-title {
				font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--amber-glow);
				margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem 0;
			}

			.info-card {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.05), rgba(0, 172, 193, 0.05));
				border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
				border-radius: 15px;
				padding: 2rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				position: relative;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.info-card::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: -100%;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.1), transparent);
				transition: left 0.6s ease;
			}

			.info-card:hover::before {
				left: 100%;
			}

			.info-card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.15);
				border-color: var(--teal-crystal);
			}

			.skill-card {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.08), rgba(0, 172, 193, 0.08));
				border: 1px solid var(--amber-glow);
				border-radius: 15px;
				padding: 2rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
			}

			.skill-card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.15);
				border-color: var(--teal-crystal);
			}

			.stats-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
			}

			.stat-item {
				background: var(--bg-secondary);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
			}

			.stat-item:hover {
				border-color: var(--amber-glow);
				transform: translateY(-2px);
			}

			.stat-label {
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--amber-glow);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.stat-value {
				color: var(--text-primary);
				font-size: 1.1rem;
			}

			.awakening-card {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.1), rgba(0, 172, 193, 0.1));
				border: 1px solid var(--amber-glow);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}

			.warning-box {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1), rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.1));
				border: 1px solid #ffc107;
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
			}

			.warning-box .warning-title {
				color: #ffc107;
				font-weight: 600;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.class-showcase {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.1), rgba(0, 172, 193, 0.1));
				border: 1px solid var(--amber-glow);
				border-radius: 15px;
				padding: 2rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				position: relative;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.class-showcase::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: -100%;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.1), transparent);
				transition: left 0.6s ease;
			}

			.class-showcase:hover::before {
				left: 100%;
			}

			.class-showcase:hover {
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.15);
				border-color: var(--teal-crystal);
			}

			.class-image {
				width: 64px;
				height: 64px;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--amber-glow);
				flex-shrink: 0;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
			}

			.class-showcase:hover .class-image {
				transform: scale(1.05);
				box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(164, 120, 100, 0.3);
			}

			.class-info h3 {
				color: var(--amber-glow);
				margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
			}

			.class-info p {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.5;
			}

			/* Responsive */
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.character-container {
					padding: 0 1rem;
				}

				.character-header,
				.content-section {
					padding: 2rem;
				}

				.character-title {
					font-size: 2.5rem;
				}

				.character-image {
					width: 250px;
					height: 250px;
				}

				.stats-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}

				/* Memory Card mobile layout */
				.content-section div[style*="display: flex"] {
					flex-direction: column !important;
					align-items: center !important;
				}

				.content-section img[alt="Leviathan Memory Card"] {
					width: 100% !important;
					max-width: 250px !important;
					height: auto !important;
					margin-bottom: 1rem !important;
				}
			}

			/* Priority Classes */
			.priority-high {
				color: #ff6b6b;
				font-weight: 700;
			}

			.priority-medium {
				color: #ffd93d;
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.priority-low {
				color: #6bcf7f;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.critical-awakening {
				border-color: #ff6b6b;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.1), rgba(255, 183, 77, 0.1));
			}

			/* Animations */
			@keyframes titleGlow {
				0% { filter: brightness(1); }
				100% { filter: brightness(1.2); }
			}

			@keyframes sectionFadeIn {
				0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
				100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
			}
		</style>
	</Fragment>

	<div class="character-page">
		<div class="character-container">
			<!-- Back Button -->
			<a href="/guides/zone-nova/characters/" class="back-button">
				<span class="back-arrow">←</span>
				Back to Characters
			</a>

			<!-- Character Header -->
			<header class="character-header">
				<!-- Character Image -->
				<img src="/images/characters/Leviathan.jpg" alt="Leviathan" class="character-image" loading="lazy" />
				
				<h1 class="character-title">Leviathan</h1>
				<p class="character-subtitle">SR • Wind • Pursuit DPS</p>
			</header>

			<!-- Character Overview -->
			<section class="content-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Character Overview</h2>
				
				<!-- Class Showcase -->
				<div class="class-showcase">
					<img src="/images/characters/class/Guerrilla.jpg" alt="Guerrilla Class" class="class-image">
					<div class="class-info">
						<h3>游击使 (Guerrilla)</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="stats-grid">
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Faction</div>
						<div class="stat-value">Huájiān (花间)</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Role</div>
						<div class="stat-value">Pursuit DPS Specialist</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h3 class="subsection-title">Base Stats at Level 80</h3>
				<div class="stats-grid">
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">HP</div>
						<div class="stat-value">6,694</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Attack</div>
						<div class="stat-value">1,088</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Defense</div>
						<div class="stat-value">442</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Energy Recovery</div>
						<div class="stat-value">2.50/s</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Critical Rate</div>
						<div class="stat-value">0%</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Critical Damage</div>
						<div class="stat-value">50%</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="info-card">
					<p style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
						Leviathan is a pursuit attack specialist who excels at chaining additional attacks triggered by ally skill usage. Her unique mark-based system allows her to store and consume marks for consistent damage output, while her critical rate scaling makes her increasingly dangerous as fights progress.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Skills Section -->
			<section class="content-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>

				<div class="skill-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">⛈️ Normal Attack: Leviathan's Kiss (利维坦之吻)</h3>
					<p><strong>Level:</strong> 14 | <strong>CD:</strong> 2.0s</p>
					<p>Deals <strong>120% of Attack</strong> as wind damage to designated enemy unit</p>
				</div>

				<div class="skill-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">⚡ Auto Skill: Abyss Roar (深渊之咆哮)</h3>
					<p><strong>Level:</strong> 10+4 | <strong>CD:</strong> 5.0s</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Deals wind damage equal to <strong>120% of Attack</strong> to designated enemy unit</li>
						<li>Gains <strong>2 layers of [Mark]</strong></li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="skill-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">💥 Ultimate: Seven Deadly Sins: Jiāolú (七大罪：娇炉)</h3>
					<p><strong>Level:</strong> 10+4 | <strong>CD:</strong> 1.0s | <strong>Energy Cost:</strong> 5</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Deals wind damage equal to <strong>600% of Attack</strong> to designated enemy unit</li>
						<li>Immediately launches <strong>1 pursuit attack</strong> against target</li>
						<li><strong>Subsequent pursuit attacks do not consume marks</strong></li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="skill-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">👑 Passive: Grudge Deep Chain (怨恨深链)</h3>
					<p><strong>Level:</strong> 14</p>
					<ul>
						<li>When our allies activate skills and hit enemies, consumes <strong>1 layer of [Mark]</strong> and triggers pursuit</li>
						<li>Pursuit deals wind damage equal to <strong>180% of Attack</strong></li>
					</ul>

					<div class="warning-box">
						<div class="warning-title">📊 Mark System Explained</div>
						<p><strong>Mark Gain:</strong> Abyss Roar grants +2 marks</p>
						<p><strong>Mark Consumption:</strong> Ally skills consume 1 mark to trigger pursuit (180% ATK)</p>
						<p><strong>Ultimate Exception:</strong> Ultimate pursuit attacks don't consume marks</p>
						<p><strong>Strategy:</strong> This creates a reactive playstyle where team activity directly enhances Leviathan's damage output</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Team Composition Skill -->
			<section class="content-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Team Composition Skill</h2>

				<div class="skill-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">🏰 Combination Skill</h3>
					<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1</p>
					
					<div class="warning-box">
						<div class="warning-title">🌀 Activation Requirements</div>
						<p>Triggers when team contains <strong>2 [Huájiān] characters</strong> OR <strong>2 [Wind] characters</strong></p>
					</div>

					<div style="margin: 1rem 0;">
						<p><strong>Effect:</strong> Self damage increased by <strong>20%</strong></p>
					</div>

					<div class="info-card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
						<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-style: italic;">
							This team skill significantly boosts Leviathan's already high damage multipliers. Huájiān and Wind faction characters often have complementary kits that work well with pursuit mechanics.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Recommended Builds -->
			<section class="content-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Recommended Builds</h2>

				<h3 class="subsection-title">Rune Sets</h3>
				
				<div class="info-card">
					<h4 style="color: var(--amber-glow); margin: 0 0 1rem 0;">🌟 Primary Build (Recommended)</h4>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>4-Piece Beth (贝丝):</strong> Critical Hit Rate +6% | When HP >80%: Critical Hit Damage +24%</li>
						<li><strong>2-Piece Alpha (阿尔法符):</strong> Attack Power +8%</li>
					</ul>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic;">
						Maximizes critical potential for pursuit attacks. Synergizes perfectly with Awakening 2 and memory card.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="info-card">
					<h4 style="color: var(--teal-crystal); margin: 0 0 1rem 0;">⚡ Team Support Build</h4>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>4-Piece Epsilon (埃普西隆):</strong> Attack Power +8% | After Ultimate: Team damage +10% (10s)</li>
						<li><strong>2-Piece Beth (贝丝):</strong> Critical Hit Rate +6%</li>
					</ul>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic;">
						Provides team-wide damage boost after ultimate while maintaining personal critical scaling.
					</p>
				</div>

				<h3 class="subsection-title">Main Stats</h3>
				<div class="stats-grid">
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Position 1</div>
						<div class="stat-value">HP (Fixed)</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Position 2</div>
						<div class="stat-value">ATK (Fixed)</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Position 3</div>
						<div class="stat-value">DEF (Fixed)</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Position 4</div>
						<div class="stat-value">Crit Rate / Crit Damage / ATK%</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Position 5</div>
						<div class="stat-value">Wind Damage% / ATK%</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<div class="stat-label">Position 6</div>
						<div class="stat-value">ATK%</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h3 class="subsection-title">Substat Priorities</h3>
				<div class="info-card">
					<ol style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
						<li><strong>Critical Rate</strong> - Essential for pursuit attacks with Awakening 2</li>
						<li><strong>Critical Damage</strong> - Maximizes critical scaling potential</li>
						<li><strong>Attack %</strong> - Core scaling for all damage abilities</li>
						<li><strong>Penetration</strong> - Flat number only, helps break through enemy defenses</li>
						<li><strong>Attack (Flat)</strong> - Secondary attack scaling</li>
						<li><strong>Defense%</strong> - Survivability and defensive scaling</li>
						<li><strong>HP%</strong></li>
					</ol>
				</div>

				<div class="warning-box">
					<div class="warning-title">🎯 Critical Rate Focus</div>
					<p>Aim for 1:2 Critical Rate : Critical Damage ratio. With Awakening 2 (+20%) and Memory Card (+36%), pursuit attacks can reach very high critical rates.</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Awakening Effects -->
			<section class="content-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Awakening Effects</h2>
				
				<div class="awakening-card critical-awakening">
					<h3 class="skill-title">🌟 Awakening 1 (CRITICAL)</h3>
					<p>Self triggers <strong>[Skills]</strong> can trigger activation effects</p>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic;">Allows Leviathan's skills to benefit from various trigger-based team effects and equipment bonuses</p>
				</div>

				<div class="awakening-card critical-awakening">
					<h3 class="skill-title">🌟 Awakening 2 (CRITICAL)</h3>
					<p><strong>[Pursuit]</strong> critical rate increased by <strong>20%</strong></p>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic;">Essential for critical-focused builds, synergizes perfectly with memory card</p>
				</div>

				<div class="awakening-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">Awakening 3</h3>
					<p><strong>[Skills]</strong> and <strong>[Normal Attack]</strong> level and level cap +4</p>
				</div>

				<div class="awakening-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">Awakening 4</h3>
					<p><strong>[Pursuit]</strong> damage increased by <strong>20%</strong></p>
				</div>

				<div class="awakening-card">
					<h3 class="skill-title">Awakening 5</h3>
					<p><strong>[Ultimate]</strong> and <strong>[Passive]</strong> level and level cap +4</p>
				</div>

				<div class="awakening-card critical-awakening">
					<h3 class="skill-title">🌟 Awakening 6 (GAME-CHANGING)</h3>
					<p>When releasing <strong>[Ultimate]</strong> skills, the number of pursuit attacks triggered changes from <strong>1 to 2</strong></p>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic;">Doubles ultimate damage output - massive DPS increase that transforms her into an elite damage dealer</p>
				</div>
			</section>

